Blinkit Sales Dashboard Report
Overview
This dashboard displays a comprehensive summary of Blinkit’s sales performance across various outlets in India. Key performance indicators such as total sales, average sales, number of items, and average rating are presented, along with specific details about outlet size, location, and item categories.

Key Highlights
Total Sales: $1.20M
Average Sales: $141
Number of Items Sold: 8523
Average Customer Rating: 3.9
Outlet Establishment Trend (2010–2020)
The sales trend has fluctuated over the past decade, with a peak in 2015 at $0.20M.

