Outlet Type Performance:

Supermarket Type 1 has the highest total sales of $787.55K with an average rating of 4.

Blinkit is analyzing sales performance to optimize inventory and improve customer satisfaction. 
The dashboard reveals that Tier 3 outlets are leading in sales, despite having lower visibility compared to Tier 1 outlets. 
Additionally, Supermarket Type 1 contributes significantly to the total sales, suggesting it may offer more popular or higher-margin products. 
However, the lower average rating (3.9) indicates room for improvement in customer experience or product quality.
